Tests
-----

Create an `.env` file and put the following lines in it, replacing the asterisks
with the valid credentials for a test user on [balena-staging.com](https://balena-staging.com)

```
TEST_EMAIL=***
TEST_PASSWORD=***
```

Run the test suite by doing:

```sh
$ npm test
```

